{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"21b6c93477","title":"撼山易撼红卫兵难","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d9319bdb12","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":12,"articleId":"21b6c93477","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"d3f84b69d8","name":"清华附中红卫兵齐向东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6484ce5679","type":"title","text":"撼山易撼红卫兵难","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7485d3449c","type":"paragraph","text":"撼山易  撼红卫兵难","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"77d850d3ef","type":"paragraph","text":"清华附中红卫兵齐向东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f3a59d9b72","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.08.12","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3e1951c057","type":"paragraph","text":"红卫兵是左派组织。红卫兵是阶级队伍。红卫兵，顶天立地当中站，牛鬼蛇神心胆寒！撼山易，撼红卫兵难！","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"849f436eff","type":"paragraph","text":"地主资产阶级狗崽子们唧唧喳喳，说什么这样提不对，什么不树立毛泽东思想绝对权威啦，什么红卫兵脱离“群众”“左”倾啦，等等，等等。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ac915e9a4c","type":"paragraph","text":"这完全是胡扯！想反红卫兵就干脆点，少拐弯抹角！","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4a6ea79a87","type":"paragraph","text":"红卫兵，是毛泽东思想的忠实卫兵。你们企图把红卫兵与毛泽东思想对立起来，迷惑群众，浑水摸鱼，纯粹是痴心妄想！","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a6fa96f31","type":"paragraph","text":"红卫兵，就是对敌人造反成性。红卫兵，有缺点，有错误，这都可以批评。左派同志与革命群众说我们脱离群众，我们要虚心接受。但是地主资产阶级狗崽子们骂我们脱离“群众”，骂我们“左”，正说明我们跟他们划清了界限，敌我分明！","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d188c1d268","type":"paragraph","text":"红卫兵，究竟怎样呢？","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7078e09107","type":"paragraph","text":"红卫兵的领导，是党中央，是毛主席！！","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7ba5afd0e","type":"paragraph","text":"红卫兵的宗旨，是横扫一切牛鬼蛇神，保卫党中央，保卫毛主席，捍卫毛泽东思想！","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"defacf7e20","type":"paragraph","text":"红卫兵的主力与骨干，是对牛鬼蛇神造反成性的红五类子弟！","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ed224f8e9","type":"paragraph","text":"红卫兵的战士，有革命先辈的光荣造反血统！有对党和毛主席的赤胆忠心！有对阶级敌人的刻骨仇恨！有毛泽东思想的绝对权威！","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"82ce2ddb3a","type":"paragraph","text":"谁违背毛泽东思想，红卫兵战士就一定造他的反！","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f68075b3a4","type":"paragraph","text":"清华附中红卫兵齐向东","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d7cf11f3e","type":"paragraph","text":"1966年8月12日","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"21b6c93477","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}